Author: so_crat_ic
Text: That girl is wearing a skirt, wearing make up, throwing up, claiming abuse, causing drama, dying her hair blue. It must be for attention, they say. God forbid she do those things for herself, or just cause she felt like it. Im so tired of this excuse.  There are some people who are so conceited, so egotistical, they will do anything to keep all eyes on them. but think how unhealthy those people must be, how broken they must be. Surely they do plenty of things 'for attention'.  If you arent taking it to the extreme by exaggurating, you probably fall into the first category, and are just doing things because YOU wanted to, independent of other people.
